(1, 2, 'Intractable 3D Medical Info Visualization', '腾讯医疗3D可交互医学内容可视化项目', '/upload/imgs/1570665429_512.gif', 'An exploration project in Tencent (2018) which is a 3D medical interactive film, aim to delivery the biological knowledge and the mechanism of the medicine. ', '腾讯医疗的可视化实验性项目，使用3D技术提供医学资讯内容，药理内容的可交互视频展示。产品运行在PC设备上，用户可以通过扫描二维码远程交互和控制视角等。产品使用了AI自动生成旁白配音，云渲染，远程操控，二维码技术等。其他概念型技术集成了包括：AI语音控制，AI手势识别，VR虚拟显示和WebGL技术(Web端实现)。', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>An exploration project in Tencent (2018-2019), a 3D medical interactive film, aim to delivery the biological knowledge and the mechanism of the medicine. The product is running on PC, audiences can control the product view remotely from a QRcode. The product has integrated with <strong>AI auto-generated voiceover</strong> (read subtitles), <strong>pixel streaming</strong>, <strong>remote control</strong> and <strong>QRCode</strong>. Serial concepts were tried or applied in the product such as <strong>AI voice recognization control</strong>, <strong>webcam AI hand-gesture control</strong>, <strong>VR experience</strong>, and <strong>WebGL technology</strong>.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>In the team, I’ve been designing and developing the 2D interface, data admin page and the remote control panel with <strong>Unreal Engine</strong>. I am the UX designer, also the front-end developer. The design process is challenging, the product is explorational and unique. It’s my first-time design and coding the remote control panel to control the big screen. I’ve learned to use the web socket deploy in a remote server to communicate between a webpage with the game engine.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570665429_512.gif|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>The project was been demonstrate to approximately ten thousand people in the company public exhibition: Tencent T-day 2018 in Shenzhen, China. The purpose of the product is to show the potential of 3D visualization technology and the concept of the digital twin that could be integrated into the medical industry as well as serve the public.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><h3><strong>Demo Video</strong></h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><iframe src=|*|https://www.youtube.com/embed/89sdr8oJ_uQ|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Used of Pixel Streaming Technology:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><iframe src=|*|https://www.youtube.com/embed/_3C8Qh6vgrQ|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><h3><strong>WebGL Version Demo (Chinese)</strong></h3><h3></h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><a href=|*|https://archives.isjeff.com/yidian|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>Open Link:</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Please wait 1 minute (approx.) for 3D model fully loaded (load in background process). You might experience long loading period due to the server is located in Asia.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1571410371_919.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Database and Admin Page:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240752_838.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><h3><strong>Media Impact</strong></h3><h3></h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>推出AI智能问答助手、布局3D可视化展示，腾讯医典想让医学科普更有温度 <a href=|*|https://36kr.com/p/5207433|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://36kr.com/p/5207433</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>来腾讯T-DAY体验医疗新科技 就诊全流程智慧化全面升级 <a href=|*|https://kknews.cc/tech/3n83mng.html|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://kknews.cc/tech/3n83mng.html</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>专业的设计流程是怎样的？来看腾讯的医学可视化探索案例！<a href=|*|https://www.uisdc.com/tencent-medical-visualization-design|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://www.uisdc.com/tencent-medical-visualization-design</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><h3><strong>Tday Event</strong></h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570058424_605.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240822_997.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240823_72.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240823_386.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240893_443.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>腾讯医疗的可视化实验性项目，使用3D技术提供医学资讯内容，药理内容的可交互视频展示。产品运行在PC设备上，用户可以通过扫描二维码远程交互和控制视角等。产品使用了AI自动生成旁白配音，云渲染，远程操控，二维码技术等。其他概念型技术集成了包括：AI语音控制，AI手势识别，VR虚拟显示和WebGL技术(Web端实现)。</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>在团队中，我担任2D界面，数据管理界面和远程操控交互的设计，同时也兼部分技术开发。由于是实验项目，项目过程中充满了不同的挑战，并且这是第一次在生产项目中，通过网页使用websocket技术连接Unreal游戏引擎实现，设计和开发一个远程控制面板。</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>交互设计流程：<strong>3D医疗可视化产品的探索，展示和原型</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><a href=|*|https://isjeff.com/post?pid=50&amp;from=blog&amp;lang=0|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://isjeff.com/post?pid=50&amp;from=blog&amp;lang=0</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570665429_512.gif|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>这个项目在腾讯用户开放日TDay 2018上首次亮相，产品展示了腾讯医疗如何运用3D可视化技术，传递医学健康知识，手术过程。也展示了智慧医疗和数字孪生结合的广阔发展前景，实现公司服务大众，科技向善的目标。</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><h3>演示视频</h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><iframe src=|*|https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f3008o1tpr1|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><h3>网页3D演示：</h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><a href=|*|https://archives.isjeff.com/yidian|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>Open Link:</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Please wait 1 minute (approx.) for 3D model fully loaded (load in background process). You might experience long loading period due to the server is located in Asia.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1571410371_919.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><h3><strong>数据管理端</strong></h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240752_838.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><h3><strong>媒体影响</strong></h3><h3></h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>推出AI智能问答助手、布局3D可视化展示，腾讯医典想让医学科普更有温度 <a href=|*|https://36kr.com/p/5207433|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://36kr.com/p/5207433</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>来腾讯T-DAY体验医疗新科技 就诊全流程智慧化全面升级 <a href=|*|https://kknews.cc/tech/3n83mng.html|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://kknews.cc/tech/3n83mng.html</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>专业的设计流程是怎样的？来看腾讯的医学可视化探索案例！<a href=|*|https://www.uisdc.com/tencent-medical-visualization-design|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://www.uisdc.com/tencent-medical-visualization-design</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><h3><strong>腾讯用户开放日 Tday 2017</strong></h3><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570058424_605.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240822_997.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240823_72.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240823_386.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570240893_443.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', 1, '2019-08-21 00:00:00', '2019-11-03 17:46:03', 1310, 1180, 9, 1),
(15, 1, 'Motion Graphic and Data Visualization Design: Malcolm Campbell''s life in', '动效和数据可视化：1分钟看完马尔科姆·坎贝尔的一生', '/upload/imgs/1570746544_706.gif', 'An informatic design project demonstrate Malcolm Campbell''s life', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>This is an informatic design project demonstrate Malcolm Campbell|**|s life. Project certains information by a info-graphic poster and a 1 minute motion graphic video.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><iframe src=|*|https://www.youtube.com/embed/50TTByc_J1g|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Poster:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570109222_460.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>使用动效视频(motion graphic) 和数据海报(infographic)展示了马尔科姆·坎贝尔的生平介绍，一个多次打破世界陆地/水面速度记录的人。设计中，运用噪点noise表现历史感和庄重感。动画中大量采用简单但具有速度感画面，表现敢于追求，挑战极限的马尔科姆。</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><iframe src=|*|https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t0641trhpr4&amp;amp;tiny=0&amp;amp;auto=0|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Poster:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570109222_460.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p>', 1, '2018-04-30 12:00:00', '2019-10-24 11:10:13', 177, 2, 15, 1),
(26, 1, '3D Data Visualization for University Library by WebGL', '大学图书馆的Web端3D大数据可视化', '/upload/imgs/1570746220_40.gif', 'A 3D data visualization product for shown PC device availability in the main library of the University of Portsmouth', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>This is a 3D data visualization product for shown PC device availability in the main library of the University of Portsmouth. The product delivery real-time situation visually and helps student found connected seats for group study.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>The artefact is made by WebGL and Three.js which intractable and accessible from any modern web browser and allows users to open in various devices.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Product Demo Video:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><iframe src=|*|https://www.youtube.com/embed/0uLGM68kbmQ|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Product Demo (not real-time data):</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><a href=|*|http://archives.isjeff.com/sas/|*| class=|*|ilink__embed|*| target=|*|_blank|*| datatype=|*|link|*|>Open Link: </a><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570239290_790.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570239321_658.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570239342_120.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570239337_351.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570239308_668.jpg|*| wi