(27, 1, 'Dynamic Web Design and Development for A Cinema Ticket Booking Website', '影院在线购票系统的网站设计与原型开发', '/upload/imgs/1570288538_356.jpg', 'A dynamic web project for cinema online ticket booking service.', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>A dynamic web project for cinema online ticket booking service. The project delivers with UI/UX design, competing product analysis, front-end and back-end prototype. Technologies including Vue.js(PWA framework), Responsive CSS, Mysql database, and PHP built API in use. To complete the project requires project management, brand design, interaction and visual design, front-end and back-end development. Von Restorff effect and the Law of proximity applied in design.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570288538_356.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Role: Product Manager, UX/UI Designer(Including Logo and Icon design), Developer</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Collaborators: Liam White</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Demo Video (Desktop)</strong></p><iframe src=|*|https://www.youtube.com/embed/G7qLUzzQzdc|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Demo Video (Mobile)</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><iframe src=|*|https://www.youtube.com/embed/abfYb-t__BU|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570288650_799.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570288650_577.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%