(30, 1, 'Information Exchange App for the Oversea Chinese Student', '海外中国留学生生活信息交流平台设计和开发', '/upload/imgs/1570290827_400.jpg', 'An application built upon the WeChat mini-program framework to serve as an information exchange platform for the oversea Chinese student at the University of Portsmouth', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>This project is an application built upon the WeChat mini-program framework to serve as an information exchange platform for the oversea Chinese student at the University of Portsmouth. The product is able to display certain life-related information and alerts in the city of Portsmouth for Chinese student,  also allows users to publish or share events information such as organizing a trip or a party.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Problems:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Chinese student needs local life information.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Chinese student relies on WeChat as there social network access.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Chinese student could need an events platform to gather people for a party or a trip.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Solution:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Built a mobile application offering information, events platform.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Built on WeChat social network platform which Chinese students were easily accessing to reduce the acquisition cost and keep user retention.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Built membership system to gather user personal information to do the further business expansion.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Design Concept:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Content-Centric with no visual interference.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Big size texture and clear visual design all for presenting data only.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Reduce page navigate, all activities could be completed within 3 steps of interaction.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Technical Detail:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Font-end: WeChat Official API, JavaScript ES5</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Back-end and data API: PHP</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Database: MySQL</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Design Tools: Sketch</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Team Detail:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Individual project</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Interaction Design:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570290532_330.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>UI Design:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570290536_321.jpeg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>DEMO:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Search: 朴茨茅斯生活助手 in WeChat Mini-programme Platform</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>or scan this code</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570290661_597.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>This project is an application built upon the WeChat mini-program framework to serve as an information exchange platform for the oversea Chinese student at the University of Portsmouth. The product is able to display certain life-related information and alerts in the city of Portsmouth for Chinese student, also allows users to publish or share events information such as organizing a trip or a party.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Problems:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Chinese student needs local life information.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Chinese student relies on WeChat as there social network access.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Chinese student could need an events platform to gather people for a party or a trip.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Solution:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Built a mobile application offering information, events platform.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Built on WeChat social network platform which Chinese students were easily accessing to reduce the acquisition cost and keep user retention.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Built membership system to gather user personal information to do the further business expansion.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Design Concept:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Content-Centric with no visual interference.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Big size texture and clear visual design all for presenting data only.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Reduce page navigate, all activities could be completed within 3 steps of interaction.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Technical Detail:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Font-end: WeChat Official API, JavaScript ES5</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Back-end and data API: PHP</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Database: MySQL</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Design Tools: Sketch</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Team Detail:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Individual project</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Interaction Design:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570290532_330.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>UI Design:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570290536_321.jpeg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>DEMO:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Search: 朴茨茅斯生活助手 in WeChat Mini-programme Platform</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>or scan this code</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570290661_597.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p>', 1, '2017-10-16 03:51:25', '2019-10-13 00:26:51', 3272, 125, 21, 1),
(31, 1, 'Tencent Medical Dictionary App Design', '腾讯医典产品交互设计', '/upload/imgs/1570663822_125.gif', 'Tencent Medipedia App DesignTencent Medipedia App Design', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Tencent Yidian is a Medipedia (Medical dictionary) mobile website and App like WebMD. It was published as a non-profit product aim to spread medical science knowledge to the general public. Many design works need to be done in the process, such as user research, user experience map, interaction flow, UX wireframe. For improving efficiency and consistency, I and my colleague organized to produce a range of UX Design kits and standard design documents.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>It is quite a challenge that delivers such a big medical database to a large number of users from different age group and different education background. We|**|ve done a lot of user research, and try to implement universal design and draw different style of illustrations.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570659287_636.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Product Screenshot Example:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570662081_613.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>UX Design Kits Example:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570661028_780.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Whiteframe Works Example:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570661214_184.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>腾讯医典是一个非盈利的医疗百科网站和APP，目标是帮助社区传播医学科普知识。 医典提供包括但不限于疾病预防信息，急救教育，在线查找医院甚至心理疾病自测。医学资讯类产品的设计是庞大且复杂的，我们的工作包含大量的用户研究，体验地图，交互流程研究等。为了提升效率，团队组建了各类设计控件库和标准化的设计规范。</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>将大量的医学信息传达给大量处在不同年龄层，不同教育水平和收入阶层的用户是非常具有挑战性的，我们对此进行了大量的用户研究，尝试了各种包容的界面设计和不同的插图风格。</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570659287_636.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Product Screenshot Example:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570662081_613.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>UX Design Kits Example:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570661028_780.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Whiteframe Works Example:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570661214_184.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', 1, '2019-10-05 15:55:41', '2019-10-19 23:38:30', 399, 25, 11, 1),
(32, 1, 'Break The Fourth Wall Convention in AI Conversational Interface Design', '打破第四面墙：在对话式AI设计中的运用', '/upload/imgs/1570372835_161.jpg', 'The fourth wall is a performance art convention which descript the invisible barrier between audiences and actors. In this project, I''ve tried to integrate the fourth wall theory into the AI conversational design process, to figure out how to mitigate the negative Human-AI conversation experience which brings by the poor AI machine recognize technology.', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>The fourth wall is a performance art convention which descript the invisible barrier between audiences and actors. In this project, I|**|ve tried to integrate the fourth wall theory into the AI conversational design process, to figure out how to mitigate the negative Human-AI conversation experience which brings by the poor AI machine recognize technology.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>This research has been done when I am doing internship work on Tencent Inc. during the time 05.2017 - 09.2017. The original report was written in Chinese, the content was translated directly from Chinese to English. There might be some content will be not easy to comprehend by the result of translation but the main concept and idea remained.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570372835_161.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570373075_627.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570372930_964.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570373207_784.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570372887_270.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p