(33, 3, 'Music Streaming Products non-invasive Sync Playlist UX sulution  ', '音乐产品非侵入式歌单导入交互方案', '/upload/imgs/1570531628_73.png', 'An idea of Non-invasive music straming Apps playlist sync to the other music Apps by using screenshot+OCR technology.', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>An idea of Non-invasive music straming Apps playlist sync to the other music Apps by using screenshot+OCR technology. The English version is next to Chinese version.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570531358_825.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|> <img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570531462_769.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>An idea of Non-invasive music straming Apps playlist sync to the other music Apps by using screenshot+OCR technology. The English version is next to Chinese version.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570531358_825.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|> <img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570531462_769.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', 1, '2017-09-11 10:46:14', '2019-10-24 14:07:10', 128, 21, 25, 1),
(34, 1, 'Night Out Activities Planner Mobile App Project', '夜生活APP设计和开发项目', '/upload/imgs/1570532661_142.jpg', '', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>This is a prototype done for individual clients who want to start up an internet company that change the way people manage their night out activities. The product aims to deliver need to know information for an unbeatable night out experience, including the functions of display nearby events, planning night out venues and social ability. The challenge is our client require an entire solution including brand document, Ad mockup, UX/UI design and an Android application. I have learned Android App development and complete 90% of the application programming (Front-end and back-end).</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Role in the team: UX designer, visual designer, Android developer</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><br><strong>Project Aim:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>To develop the <em>Out Out</em> app that delivers need to know information for an unbeatable night out.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Regarding client information and market research, the team will need to construct a full end to end analysis of the <em>Out Out</em> experience.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Objectives:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Identify existing market competitors and target audience.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Develop location intelligence to build meaningful user experiences and potential business/advertising solutions.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Integration with existing channels and user touchpoints.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Demo:</p><iframe src=|*|https://www.youtube.com/embed/RV4Y9TlL0fE|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Technical Detail:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Building Tools: Android Studio</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Language: Java</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>API: built by php+mysql</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Brand Document:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570532661_142.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Download: <a href=|*|https://api.isjeff.com/pot/upload/files/1570532708_390.pdf|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://api.isjeff.com/pot/upload/files/1570532708_390.pdf</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>UX Design 交互设计</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570532836_229.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570532859_369.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><em>Design Tools: Adobe Illustrator &amp; Adobe Photoshop</em></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>这个项目是大学跨学科课程的课程作业，内容是帮助一位校外客户完成他的一个项目。项目内容：OutOut是一个夜生活APP，主要目的是帮助用户查找/计划夜生活活动，口号是帮助用户打造最完美的夜生活，主打社交领域功能。在本项目中我担任品牌设计师，用户交互设计师和前后端开发人员。本产品90%的功能由我独立开发完成。</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>团队角色：交互设计，视觉设计，Android开发</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><br><strong>设计目标:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>使用OUTOUT计划一个完美的夜晚</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>基于市场研究和商业目标，构建一个端到端的完整体验</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>实现路径:</strong></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>定义目标客户和市场竞品</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>开发基于地理位置信息的用户交互体验，提供市场营销解决方案</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>集成现有渠道，用户触点</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>演示视频：</p><iframe src=|*|https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=x0642nnpvqr&amp;amp;tiny=0&amp;amp;auto=0|*| width=|*|600px|*| height=|*|300px|*| frameborder=|*|0|*| allowfullscreen=|*|true|*|></iframe><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>技术细节:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>工具: Android Studio</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>语言: Java</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>API接口: php+mysql</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>品牌VI文档:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570532661_142.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>下载完整文档: <a href=|*|https://api.isjeff.com/pot/upload/files/1570532708_390.pdf|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://api.isjeff.com/pot/upload/files/1570532708_390.pdf</a></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>UX Design 交互设计</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570532836_229.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570532859_369.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', 1, '2018-03-07 11:04:52', '2019-10-24 13:50:41', 245, 4, 26, 1),
