(36, 1, 'Portsmouth city Chinese new year celebration design project 2018', '朴茨茅斯中国学联2018年春节晚会海报和舞台背景设计', '/upload/imgs/1570649022_151.gif', 'This project was done for a performance event which to celebrate annual new year gala on 05 of February when I am working for CSSA (Chinese student & scholar Association) organization. This performance is one of the largest events in the city Portsmouth for celebrating the Chinese New Year for local Chinese and oversea student community, many important people from the politic and military area were attended including the mayor himself.', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>This project was done for a performance event which to celebrate annual new year gala on 05 of February when I am working for CSSA (Chinese student &amp; scholar Association) organization. This performance is one of the largest events in the city Portsmouth for celebrating the Chinese New Year for local Chinese and oversea student community, many important people from the politic and military area were attended including the mayor himself.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>This project is a huge and integral</strong> <strong>stage design with a range of graphic design and motion graphic/music visualization, stage background design and lighting. I and my team accomplished a very successful, highly sophisticated event, closely work with the University, local Chinese society and HK student society.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Role in team: President of Chinese student and scholar association, Graphic and motion graphic designer</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Materials:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570535033_124.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570649022_151.gif|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570630559_258.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Poster Design:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570535108_452.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>朴茨茅斯中国学生学者联谊会 2018年中国春节晚会海报和舞台背景设计，英国朴茨茅斯本地最大的华人节日活动，涉及上千名观众，市长，重要政客和学校领导到场。项目涉及一系列的平面，动效和舞台设计。项目与大学，本地华人协会和中国香港学生组织一起完成。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>团队角色: CSSA学生会主席, 视觉设计</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>设计工作:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570535033_124.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570649022_151.gif|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570630559_258.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Poster Design:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570535108_452.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', 1, '2018-03-08 12:00:00', '2019-10-24 13:54:06', 37, 24, 24, 1);
