(42, 3, 'Pucun-Takeaway Project', '可能是英国首个华人外卖尝试：朴村外卖', '/upload/imgs/1570881665_592.jpg', 'Pucun-Takeaway is an O2O business website. This might be the first Chinese takeaway order online platform in the UK. Since the website published, it has 90 registered users and 40 orders, work with 6 commercial. (until 05.18.2016). This service was closed now.', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Pucun-Takeaway is an O2O business website. This might be the first Chinese takeaway order online platform in the UK. Since the website published, it has 90 registered users and 40 orders, work with 6 commercial. (until 05.18.2016). <strong>This service was closed now.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><ul><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Objective:</strong> a web-application for order Chinese takeaway Online in Portsmouth, UK</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Target Group:</strong> Chinese oversea student at the University of Portsmouth.</p></li><li><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Marketing strategy:</strong> Use social media platform provide life information in Portsmouth city, targeting the fresher Chinese oversea student who just comes to the University of Portsmouth. By providing the information, convert them into our follower in social media account. Use the social media platform to promote the takeaway service, close the system lifecycle.</p></li></ul><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Functions:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- Browsing nearby restaurant that offers takeaway service.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- Order takeaway</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- Order management page</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- User can search and add items to the shopping cart.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- Restaurant side can modify menu.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- The User order flow: Select item from the menu to shopping cart -&gt; Confirm order (Insert to database, Send Email to user) -&gt; Wating for restrants confirmation -&gt; Confirm item received -&gt; Give a mark for the service.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- The Restaurant Side order flow: Get Email / SMS in Phone -&gt; Login to Order Center -&gt; Click Confirm order -&gt; Click order has been send -&gt; Wating for user confirmation.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- Restaurant can set discount.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- Support SMS / Email notification.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>-- Mobile Device Compatibility (Responsive Design)</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Screenshot:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570881169_908.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570881565_279.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570881589_897.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>In-store promotion:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570881665_592.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570881726_460.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Coupon Design:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570881638_532.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', '', 1, '2016-05-18 11:55:32', '2019-10-13 00:25:30', 432, 12, 20, 1);
