(44, 3, 'LiveFACE Start Up Project ', 'LiveFACE 创业项目', '/upload/imgs/1570924062_142.jpg', 'LiveFACE Project is a start-up project with business purpose found by me started on Feb.2013 and end on Dec.2015 when I was in senior high school. Our goal is to build an Internet services ecosystem in Android platform like XIAOMI. During the project, we build an Android base third-party operation system (ROM), We build an Android Launcher application, a technology blog website and online BBS forum for our user.', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE Project is a start-up project with business purpose found by me started on Feb.2013 and end on Dec.2015 when I was in senior high school. Our goal is to build an Internet services ecosystem in Android platform like XIAOMI. During the project, we build an Android base third-party operation system (ROM), We build an Android Launcher application, a technology blog website and online BBS forum for our user.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>An Android-based operation system (ROM), an Android application package, a technology blog website and a user BBS website.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570923975_683.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570749711_78.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924001_510.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE ROM: an Android-based operation system (ROM). It has a serious new function in Android original operating system and adapted to 10+ Android devices. I am the project manager, team leader and UI designer in this project.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>The main function example: our ROM|**|s status bar can identify the software top-tab and change colour itself (in Android 4.4 !!! ). It doesn|**|t need software to adapted our system.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924017_639.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924048_823.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924062_142.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE LAUNCHER is an Android application which develops for LiveFACE ROM but independent publish in the app market. The launcher is a desktop or basic application entrance for any Android user.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE LAUNCHER and other system application package:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE Launcher: <a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.face|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.face</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE_CM Theme: <a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.cmtheme|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.cmtheme</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE BOX：<a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.liveface.abox|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.liveface.abox</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE OneDay：<a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.flydev.oneday|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.flydev.oneday</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>We had an online team with 20+ member at the time.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>The last logo:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924176_772.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>And we hold an offline party with our partner once. Hold in July of 2015, NetValley cafe Shekou, Shenzhen, Guangdong, China.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570749648_884.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>RESULT:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>This group dismiss on June 2015 because we bump into a bottleneck and I started my University life. We started at a 3 mate team end at 20 people online team and have 70000+ user and also keep 200+ user who very supports us in social media. In this period of time, I learn web and application user interface design, some web development skill, (online) team running skill, social media PR skill, project manager skill and software product design (including function and user interface) skill. It|**|s hard to say that skill is highly professional or academy but I still believe that is an experience I can not forget in my entire life.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>And we publish our source code at last in the OSC code community.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE LAUNCHER Open Source Project :</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://github.com/isjeffcom/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://github.com/isjeffcom/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE Theme For CyanogenMod OS 12/12.1 :</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_CMTheme|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_CMTheme</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE BOX Open Source Project:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/abox|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/abox</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE OneDay Open Source Project:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/oneday|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/oneday</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE 项目是一个由我发起的，有着商业目的，幼稚的创业项目，存在于2013－2015年，我个人的高中时期。我们的目标是建设一个像小米公司一样，基于Android的互联网生态平台。在这个非正式的创业计划当中，我们打造了一个Android第三方ROM，开发了一个Android第三方Launcher启动器（桌面美化）应用。一个科技博客网站，和用户技术社区。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>一个基于Android的第三方操作系统（ROM），一套应用程序包，一个科技博客网站和一个用户社区。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE ROM: 一个基于Android的第三方操作系统（ROM），带有一系列相对于原生Android应用层面的改进。项目中，我担任产品经理，团队队长和设计师。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570923975_683.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570749711_78.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924001_510.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>主要功能案例：ROM状态栏色彩变化自适应（在Android 4.4上实现！！）。无需第三方软件适配。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924017_639.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924048_823.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924062_142.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE 启动器（桌面）是一个为LiveFACE ROM开发的独立安卓应用。启动器是任何Android用户的基础桌面应用和应用打开入口。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE LAUNCHER 启动器和其他独立发布的系统应用 （可能已下架）：</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE Launcher （启动器）: <a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.face|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.face</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE_CM Theme（CM主题）: <a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.cmtheme|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cc.flydev.cmtheme</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE BOX（盒子）：<a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.liveface.abox|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.liveface.abox</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE OneDay（一天）：<a href=|*|https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.flydev.oneday|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.flydev.oneday</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>科技新闻网站 :</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924407_14.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>我们曾经有20个以上的在线团队的成员。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>最后一个LOGO</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924176_772.png|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>举办线下沙龙派对，举办与2015年7月份，地点：深圳蛇口网谷</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570749648_884.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>结局：</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>团队与2015年7月因为遇到不可逾越的瓶颈解散，我个人进入大学生活。我们从3个人的团队做到20个人的在线工作室。我们最高有7万名用户和200个非常忠实的用户到现在已然在支持我们。这是我一生无法忘却的经历，在那段时间当中，我学到了网页，UI设计，一些网页开发技能，线上线下团队运营能力，活动举办能力，社交媒体运营能力和获取了一些企业公关经验。很难说这些技能是非常专业或学术的，但我确实从中学到了很多。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>我们最终将大部分成果开源。</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE LAUNCHER Open Source Project 启动器开源项目:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://github.com/isjeffcom/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://github.com/isjeffcom/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_LAUNCHER-OSP</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE Theme For CyanogenMod OS 12/12.1 CM主题开源项目:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_CMTheme|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/LiveFACE_CMTheme</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE BOX Open Source Project 盒子开源项目:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/abox|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/abox</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>LiveFACE OneDay Open Source Project 一天开源项目t:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong><a href=|*|https://git.oschina.net/liveface/oneday|*| rel=|*|noopener noreferrer nofollow|*|>https://git.oschina.net/liveface/oneday</a></strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p>', 1, '2016-05-20 12:00:00', '2019-10-22 10:22:25', 255, 12, 8, 1),
(45, 3, 'Single Party Poster Design 2016', '单身派对海报设计 2016', '/upload/imgs/1570924738_954.jpg', 'This project is an event poster design for CSSA (Chinese student & scholar Association) annual single party on 11 of November. Including poster, banner and ticket design. I am the role of leader and graphic designer in the project.', '', '<p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>This project is an event poster design for CSSA (Chinese student &amp; scholar Association) annual single party on 11 of November. Including poster, banner and ticket design. I am the role of leader and graphic designer in the project.</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Main Poster:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924644_94.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Main Poster 2:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924679_818.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Ticket Design: Male will get a Female ticket and female will get a male ticket.</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Front:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924738_954.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|>Back:</p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924691_351.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|[%base%]/upload/imgs/1570924722_571.jpg|*| width=|*|100%|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><strong>Social Network Promotion Banner:</strong></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|></p><p style=|*|text-align: left|*|><img src=|*|